**`app/auth.py`** — `require_api_key` now reads `X-API-Key`, validates against `VALID_API_KEYS`, raises `HTTP 401` if missing/invalid, and returns the username.

**`app/main.py`** — rewritten with all features:

| Endpoint | What it does |
|---|---|
| `GET /projects` | Unchanged |
