| `GET /tasks/{task_id}` | Unchanged |
| `POST /tasks` | Requires auth. Validates `project_id` exists (404 if not). Auto-generates `id`. Returns 201 with the created task. |
| `PUT /tasks/{task_id}` | Requires auth. Partial update via `TaskUpdate` model. Returns 404 if not found. |
